### Register
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "password": "Password@123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "password": "Password@123"
}

### Create advice
POST http://localhost:8080/api/advice
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Stay hydrated",
  "text": "Drink water regularly",
  "category": "health"
}

### Rate advice
POST http://localhost:8080/api/advice/1/rate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 5
}

### Search
GET http://localhost:8080/api/advice/search?q=water&category=health&page=0&size=10&sort=createdAt,DESC

### Top rated
GET http://localhost:8080/api/advice/top-rated?page=0&size=10

